data.description: Look No Further!!! This beautiful multi-level home on heavily landscaped 2.5-acre lot at the end of the cul-de-sac is waiting for you to call home! Beautiful hardwood floors in the kitchen as well as large rec room/den/bonus room w/bar. Spacious great room with fireplace and vaulted ceiling, two decks, plus sunroom off garage is perfect for home office, craft or exercise room. The kitchen has upgraded appliances with granite counters and soft close drawers. All of the rooms are very spacious and the master features 2 closets with one being a walk in. This is a dynamite home just waiting for you to add your own personal touch.
